    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001650/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The subject is organized so that the students can obtain a knowledge regarding the EMI and EMC, with a special emphasis on applications in power converters. EMI filters for three phase rectifiers will be analyzed in detail.
The idea is to form students to be capable of understanding the origin of all the mechanisms that generate electromagentic noise (conducted and radiated), so that they can make optimized and reliable designs."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/miroslav.vasic%40upm.es> ;
